Fluxbox is a windowmanager for X. It is light on resources yet full of features.
Fluxbox sourcecode is distributed under an MIT license.
Fluxbox was derived from the Blackbox v0.61.1 code.

For copyright information, see COPYING.
For more information, visit:    http://fluxbox.org/

Read INSTALL to read about building and installing fluxbox.
Read NEWS to see whats new in this release...
...er, as of this writing, recent devnotes are not yet
contained within one single file, so
also refer to "debian/changelog" within the source tree
